Sentencas: Calcium co-doped SDC-based nanocomposite electrolyte (Ce0.8Sm0.2-xCaxO2-delta-Na2CO3) was synthesized by a co-precipitation method.
Titulo: Study on calcium and samarium co-doped ceria based nanocomposite electrolytes

Sentencas: The microstructure and morphology of the composite electrolytes were characterized by X-ray diffraction (XRD), scanning electron microscope (SEM), and transmission electron microscope (TEM), and thermal properties were determined with differential scanning calorimetry (DSC).
Titulo: Study on calcium and samarium co-doped ceria based nanocomposite electrolytes

Sentencas: The particle size, as shown by TEM imaging, was 5-20 nm, which is in a good agreement with the SEM and XRD results.
Titulo: Study on calcium and samarium co-doped ceria based nanocomposite electrolytes

Sentencas: The co-doping effect on both interfaces of the composite electrolyte and doped bulk effect inside the ceria was studied.
Titulo: Study on calcium and samarium co-doped ceria based nanocomposite electrolytes

Sentencas: The excellent performance of the fuel cell was about 1000 mW cm(-2) at 560 degrees C and at the very low temperature of 350 degrees C the power density was 200 mW cm(-2).
Titulo: Study on calcium and samarium co-doped ceria based nanocomposite electrolytes

Sentencas: This paper may give a new approach to develop functional nanocomposite electrolyte for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cell (LTSOFC).
Titulo: Study on calcium and samarium co-doped ceria based nanocomposite electrolytes
